Launching "The Selformation Podcast" ğŸ™ï¸ tomorrow at 1pm GMT time! Posting an episode a week -- each episode will cover the different inner work/self concept messages behind the 1/1 art pieces I have created for my #NFT collection I am launching with @MatildaColman @AmbodiXYZ

The space definitely taught me to trust myself even when others keep telling me "it's too risky" or "it makes no sense", how to find my own balance, and being okay with not always being able to keep up. I also made some incredible friends through here... and that's invaluable

It was exhausting to keep up with. We've seen some amazing creators like the @meta_angels team and @zaingaziani protect their community and team so they won't feel like they are on the verge of mental burnout. We want to be a part of changing this conversation too.

Then I sold 1 VF, made some really good and questionable investing moves (but that's a story for another time), @MatildaColman and I decided we'd be doing 1/1 NFT pieces on Procreate... all while trying to juggle this with my other pre-existing commitments

Started brainstorming ideas with @MatildaColman around late June/early July to see how we could bring #NFTs into our small business. The initial designs were animated trading cards.. so I learnt the basics of Adobe After Effects (which also changed a lot in a period of two weeks) https://t.co/8nWO8D3S6D

I definitely took a leap of confidence in myself and trusted my gut feeling... so I pulled the trigger and invested in 2 @veefriends in May 2021 (who remembers this crazy launch?! ğŸ˜…) https://t.co/bdoBAwogfO

It's insane to think that it's been just over a year since I got involved in the #NFT space. I first learnt about NFTs after watching @garyvee talk about it (+ saw a few CH rooms on it). Here's how it has changed my life ğŸ§µ
